<introduction>
<p>
A human being who is <m>h</m> feet tall is walking away from a streetlamp that is <m>l</m> feet tall  at <m>v</m> feet per second. Find the rate at which the length of the human's shadow is increasing if:
</p>
</introduction>
<task>
<statement>
<p>
<m>h=10</m>, <m>l=5</m>, and <m>v=2</m>.
</p>
</statement>
</task>
<task>
<statement>
<p>
<m>h=17</m>, <m>l=6</m>, and <m>v=7</m>.
</p>
</statement>
</task>
<task>
<statement>
<p>
<m>h=20</m>, <m>l=4</m>, and <m>v=10</m>.
</p>
</statement>
</task>
<task>
<statement>
<p>
<m>h=h</m>, <m>l=l</m>, and <m>v=v</m>.
</p>
</statement>
</task>
</exercise>
<exercise>
<introduction>
